  "short_text": "Exponent of a Number - 2",
  "content": "Write a program to recursively compute the value of A raised to the power B.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The first line of input will contain an integer (A). <br/>The second line of input will contain a positive integer (B).<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be a single line containing the value of A raised to power B.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given A is 2 and B is 3, the value of 2 raised to power 3 is (2 * 2 * 2). So the output should be 8.",
